column9: Donor: National Union of Rail, Maritime and Transport Workers

14 January 2011 I visited Hunterston B power station and was presented with a framed picture, approximate value £160, and a compact mirror, approximate value £20.  Hours: 1.5 hours.  Both presentations were made by EDF Energy, Exeter Business Park, EX1 3UT. (Registered 2 February 2011)
